Functions:
main()
Data: Variables for load, display, crop, dim, brighten, save, and exit
Functionality: Contains the menu and ability to change modes.
loadImage()
Input Parameter: File pointer, int rows, int columns, int field 2D array
Returned Output: None
Functionality: Loads an image from a file
displayImage()
Input Parameter: int rows, int columns, int field 2D array
Returned Output: None
Functionality: display image on screen
cropImage()
Input Parameter: int rows, int columns, int field 2D array, int rows location, int columns location
Returned Output: void
Functionality: Crops the loaded image
dimImage()
Input Parameter: int rows, int columns, int field 2D array, char dim
Returned Output: void
Functionality: Dims the loaded image
brightenImage()
Input Parameter: int rows, int columns, int field 2D array, char brighten
Returned Output: void
Functionality: Brightens the loaded image
saveImage()
Input Parameter: File pointer
Returned Output: File pointer
Functionality: Saves the image a new folder or the existing folder. Unless requested, remove the
old image and save the new image.
exitImage()
Input Parameter: int
Returned Output: None
Functionality: Exits the program
